title: [Feywrot Mire, Highland]
description: A half-buried carcass of a large, wild pig protrudes from beneath the leaf litter.  Deep, reptilian, claw-tipped prints leading away, with the drag marks of a heavy tail between them, leave little doubt as to what sealed this porcine's fate.
